    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉在选举抗议后拘留反对派人士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/venezuela-apprehends-opposition-figure-amid-election-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉爆发抗议活动，谴责总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗自我宣布的胜利，随后该国拘留了著名反对派人物弗雷迪·索佩拉诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/venezuela-apprehends-opposition-figure-amid-election-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:09:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特勤局代理局长在特朗普枪击事件后采取“纠正措施”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/acting-secret-service-director-taking-corrective-actions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的美国特勤局代理局长告诉参议员，在 7 月 13 日宾夕法尼亚州西部集会期间发生暗杀前总统唐纳德·特朗普的事件后，他正在采取“纠正措施”以加强安全计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/acting-secret-service-director-taking-corrective-actions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:01:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗告诉巴西，他将在未来几天公布委内瑞拉的选票记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/maduro-tells-brazil-he-ll-release-venezuela-election-records-in-coming-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情的巴西政府官员透露，尼古拉斯·马杜罗在会见巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦的高级顾问时承诺，将满足国际社会的要求，公布委内瑞拉选举的完整投票记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/maduro-tells-brazil-he-ll-release-venezuela-election-records-in-coming-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:50:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰因卢克石油过境禁令受到欧盟盟友的谴责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/ukraine-earns-rebuke-from-an-eu-ally-over-lukoil-oil-transit-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢森堡外交部长泽维尔·贝特尔周二表示，乌克兰应该考虑最近禁止俄罗斯主要供应国的原油过境等举措对其匈牙利和斯洛伐克等邻国的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/ukraine-earns-rebuke-from-an-eu-ally-over-lukoil-oil-transit-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:44:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>几内亚宪法草案将总统任期缩短至五年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/guinea-cuts-president-s-term-to-five-years-in-draft-constitution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几内亚军事领导层在一份宪法草案中提议将世界最大铝土矿出口国的总统任期从六年缩短至五年，并对其进行限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/guinea-cuts-president-s-term-to-five-years-in-draft-constitution</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党为建造更多住房而修改规划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/labour-fleshes-out-planning-changes-in-bid-to-build-more-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国副首相安格拉·雷纳 (Angela Rayner) 表示，英国新政府将让地方议会更容易在绿化带上建设住房并恢复强制性的当地住房目标，她进一步充实了工党在本届议会期间每年提供 30 万套新住房的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/labour-fleshes-out-planning-changes-in-bid-to-build-more-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>囚犯遭虐待指控动摇以色列战争团结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/soldier-arrests-for-alleged-gaza-abuse-shake-israel-s-war-unity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防部长指责政府中的极右翼同行鼓励抗议逮捕涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦囚犯的士兵，从而破坏了国家的战争努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/soldier-arrests-for-alleged-gaza-abuse-shake-israel-s-war-unity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:42:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国增加可再生能源预算至创纪录的 15 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-boosting-budget-for-renewables-to-record-1-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将在即将举行的拍卖会上将对新可再生能源发电的支持增加至创纪录的 15 亿英镑（19 亿美元），这向政府绿色计划的关键行业发出了明确信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-boosting-budget-for-renewables-to-record-1-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 10:11:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国接受摩洛哥对西撒哈拉的统治，激怒阿尔及利亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/france-recognizes-moroccan-rule-of-western-sahara-in-major-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国承认摩洛哥对西撒哈拉的主权，这一历史性转变可能刺激对有争议的矿产资源丰富的领土的更多投资，但却加剧了与邻国阿尔及利亚的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/france-recognizes-moroccan-rule-of-western-sahara-in-major-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:00:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯加大力度在摇摆州与特朗普竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/harris-team-sees-expanded-electoral-map-in-race-against-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯于周二在亚特兰大举行集会，拉开在更广泛的战场州与共和党人唐纳德·特朗普竞争的序幕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/harris-team-sees-expanded-electoral-map-in-race-against-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
